title: LEE RITENOUR Interview at the Porgy & Bess Vienna - 13 May 2013
description: Interview with guitar legend LEE RITENOUR on the occasion of his concert at the Porgy & Bess jazz club in Vienna on 13 May 2013. GuitarMania talked with Lee about his  record "Rhythm Sessions" released in 2012, and the Rhythm Section Competition. We also discussed his equipment, Fender and Mesa Boogie amplifiers, Rodenberg and Line 6 pedals, as well as the Lehle switching system. Lee also gave some piece of advice for young and aspiring musicians towards the end of the interview. GuitarMania would like to thank Heidi Meyer, Paul Goldman and the team of the Porgy & Bess. www.guitarmania.eu
